    "en": {
      "title": "Two groups of activists beat each other at the Prime Minister's office",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior spokesman said that ten people who were injured in a clash between two groups of protesters inside the Kollupitiya temple complex have been admitted to the Colombo National Hospital.",
        "He said that nine men and one woman are among them",
        "An officer of the Kollupitiya police said that a conflict had arisen during the inquiries made to the Kollupitiya police and that officers would be dispatched to the place shortly for investigation."
      ],
